---
// BentoIntro.astro — 首页 Hero 介绍卡（占据大格）
---

<div class="sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-2 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-(--radius-card) p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-between bg-gradient-to-br from-(--color-surface-900) to-(--color-surface-950) border border-(--color-surface-800)">
  <!-- 装饰性光晕 -->
  <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-72 h-72 rounded-full bg-(--color-brand-500)/10 blur-3xl group-hover:bg-(--color-brand-500)/20 transition-all duration-700"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10">
    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-(--color-brand-400) mb-6">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-(--color-brand-400) animate-pulse"></span>
      Available for work
    </span>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-(family-name:--font-heading) font-medium tracking-tight text-(--color-surface-50) leading-[1.05]">
      Shaping digital<br />
      experiences through<br />
      <span class="text-(--color-brand-400)">motion</span> & pixels.
    </h1>
  </div>

  <p class="relative z-10 text-(--color-surface-400) text-base md:text-lg max-w-md mt-6">
    👋 我是卢忠彦，一名视觉设计师。这里记录我的视觉实验与深度的设计思考。
  </p>
</div>
